name: <str::iter::Chars<'_> as iter::traits::iterator::Iterator>::flat_map::<char::EscapeUnicode, str::CharEscapeUnicode>
src:
fn flat_map<U, F>(self, f: F) -> FlatMap<Self, U, F>
    where
        Self: Sized,
        U: IntoIterator,
        F: FnMut(Self::Item) -> U,
    {
        FlatMap::new(self, f)
    }
